OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBig rise in long-term sick 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhitting UK workforce       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK risks a shrinking workforce     
OL,6, caused by long-term sickness, a new    
OL,7, report warns.                          
OL,9,FPensions and health consultants Lane,  
OL,10,FClark and Peacock (LCP) says there has 
OL,11,Fbeen a sharp increase in "economic     
OL,12,Finactivity" - working-age adults who   
OL,13,Fare not in work or looking for jobs.   
OL,15,FThe figure has risen by 516,000 since  
OL,16,FCovid hit, and early retirement does   
OL,17,Fnot appear to explain it.              
OL,19,FThe total of long-term sick, meanwhile,
OL,20,Fhas gone up by 353,000, says LCP.      
